Description: # basic-pipeline
        basic-pipeline (or *bpipe*) is a minimal &amp; simple pipeline engine for Python
        
        - [Getting Started](#getting-started)
          - [Examples](#examples)
          - [Installation](#installation)
          - [Tests](#tests)
        - [Tutorial](#tutorial)
